            "heading": "Book a In-Person Consultation.",
            "text": "<p>For those who prefer a tactile experience, we offer Private Home Visits directly to you in {{ page.metafields.custom.location.value }}. Alternatively, join us in our Chichester showroom to sit down with our master goldsmiths and view diamonds under magnification.</p>",
