            "grid_image_size": "wide",
            "heading": "Design Your Ring Online.",
            "text": "<p>Step into the role of the designer. Our innovative online studio brings the Griffin & Co workshop directly to your screen in {{ page.metafields.custom.location.value }}. Select your ideal GIA-certified diamond, choose your setting, and watch your future heirloom come to life in breathtaking 3D detail.</p>",
