            "grid_image_size": "wide",
            "heading": "Design at Home.",
            "text": "<p>Ask for a visit from our head jeweller to help you design your perfect engagement ring from the comfort of your home in {{ page.metafields.custom.location.value }}; you can see the samples in person, see 3D renders and compare different styles & gem cuts.</p>",
            "button_link": "shopify://pages/home-visits",
